THE
  BABY'S
    OWN
      ÆSOP


Being the Fables Condensed in Rhyme
with Portable Morals
Pictorially Pointed
by

WALTER CRANE







Engraved & Printed in Colours by
Edmund Evans

London
Frederick Warne and Co.
and New York




