PREFACE


For this rhymed version of the Fables I have to thank my early friend
and master W.J. LINTON, who kindly placed the MS. at my disposal. I
have added a touch here and there, but the credit of this part of the
book still belongs to him.

Walter Crane

[Illustration: ENGRAVER EE & PRINTER]




[Illustration]

To the
  Possessors of
    "Baby's Opera"
&
    "Baby's Bouquet"
with
  Walter Crane's
    Compliments




